title: Big.Brother.UK.Series.8.Disc.1.Days.001a-015b
description:
Big Brother United Kingdom Series 8

Some notes to anyone not familiar with how I post these series:
I have these series archived on dual layer dvd's which hold 
8gb each. I post them 1 disc at a time and wait for it to be 
well seeded before I move on to the next one. The last couple 
of series that I posted seemed to have the majority of
leechers disconnect as soon as they finished a disc. Please 
have the courtesy to at least give back 1 to 1 before you 
disconnect and if you can then please stay connected even 
longer. I always end up seeding a minimum of 5 to 1 and even
more when I don't get much help. This series is 54gb so I'll
end up at least seeding 300gb so I really need your help. 

This series is 7 discs so again PLEASE SEED!

This series also includes Little Brother, Big Mouth and
On the Couch!
